flowchart TD
  A[Order Delivered] --> B{Buyer satisfied?}
  B -- Yes --> C[Close order normally]
  B -- No --> D[Open dispute: /orders/{id}/disputes]
  D --> E[Collect evidence: photos, messages, tracking]
  E --> F{Seller response within SLA?}
  F -- Yes --> G[Negotiate resolution: refund/partial/return]
  F -- No --> H[Auto-escalate to Moderator]
  G --> I{Resolved?}
  I -- Yes --> J[Close dispute + apply outcome]
  I -- No --> H
  H --> K[Moderator decision + audit log]
  K --> J
